│ 462 /// Returns true if we can profitably unroll the multi-exit loop L.       │
│ Currently,                                                                    │
│ 463 /// we return true only if UnrollRuntimeMultiExit is set to true.         │
│ 464 static bool canProfitablyRuntimeUnrollMultiExitLoop(                      │
